Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊~ 好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 振作点 不要睡下去了 我们还有山要爬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不行了 日向 你就算一个人也要前进!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.21,0:01:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到达顶锋同时女生魅力也会上升
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就一个人去变成万人迷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷迷迷倒万人~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:29.83,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,等...等一下 日向!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.95,0:01:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住 我们一起登山的那个约定呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷 开着空调睡着了...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫雪村葵 现在读高一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前一直只有户内爱好的我 最近也对登山有了兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在冬天的富士山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丢下我一个人跑了 日向还真无情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么万人迷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你随便做个梦就来抱怨这也太...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日有所见夜有所梦才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我服了我服了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 回忆中的山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快来 准备搭帐篷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是日向 算是我的青梅竹马吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邀我去登山的 就是她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:35.71,Neta,NTP,0,0,0,,注:日本登山者把山划为十合目, 一合目就是山脚, 五合目山腰, 依此类推
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二季 新第一合目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住帐篷吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的帐篷能睡下四个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折起来的时候就显得特别小巧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而摊开的话可是很大的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 来搭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人能行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很轻松的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把支架穿过套管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支架?套管?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是套管 然后将作为帐篷骨骼的支架穿过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再来一根
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把支架的尖端插在锁环上面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后还差一步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搭这么大的帐篷感觉却意外简单呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说为什么在日向家后院搭起了帐篷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:35.67,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(496,10)}真的好大啊       对吧对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在山上露营?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫上心夏和枫 四个人一起住帐篷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 感觉很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事 饭还没做好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定下次和朋友一起去露营
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露营?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用饭盒做饭 睡在帐篷...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说和大家一起 是指和女生一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就住日向家怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话有她爸爸在 所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要给别人添麻烦就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就成了在日向家后院露营了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 来打桩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 打狗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是哈巴狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:29.00,Neta,NTP,0,0,0,,注:小葵把peg误认为成了pug
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,peg是指桩子 就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桩子就说桩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向外斜一点 然后打扎实了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后把拉绳套在上面 把全体固定起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就完成了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好好搭起来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小事一桩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这样看起来就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好宽敞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以放开手脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 枫姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两位是驴友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我们大一级的枫姐 她也是我们登山的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:13.62,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是宽敞呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一位是初中生心夏 女生魅力很足 是治愈系女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:19.91,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好漂亮的房子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我买了晚饭的食材过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姐 你有做过的经验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是会一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淘好米后先加水泡一泡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是用的烤肉架 开始火慢慢加 中间再烧旺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是古人用来教煮饭技巧的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算婴儿哭了也别急揭盖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果盖子被冲起来了 就压上板砖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就不会潽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们来做咖喱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锅里烧上油 把洋葱炒变色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变色?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后炒土豆 红萝卜 最后炒肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上水 煮!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微煮一会儿 把浊汁去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等咖哩块融化后...就完成了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上这隐藏味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会变得很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也煮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭有点煮糊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这米真香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖哩也做得很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过完全吃不出巧克力的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要有就不叫"隐藏味道"了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要再来份!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:06:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加这么多蛋黄酱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算少的了 要在山上的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先在边上找个地方放了吧 咦...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心动地向上升起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向你也真是的 不帮忙收拾一个人先跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵也快去吧 很舒服的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等...等下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都排队等着的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在别人家泡澡还真紧张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我洗完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没在能伸开手脚的缸里泡澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不错的澡堂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极乐啊极乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姐 不能这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸 先别下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姐 先穿上外衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈 抱歉抱歉 不小心拿出习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 冷不冷?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来挺宽敞 四个人进来还是有点挤了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向你再往那边靠点!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在山上小屋住时会有更挤的情况哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正逢登山季节 挤得像上班高峰的地铁一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样能睡着吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都累了 所以睡得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我要做荷兰酱 多放点黄油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下次也一起来做 火腿蛋松饼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来接龙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用山名来接尾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那从我开始吧 富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 刚才那个不算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,额 高尾山!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 恐山!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不对 基拉韦厄火山!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在夜深了 进入恋爱话题时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱话题?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟有四个女生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵开始吧 现在有喜欢的人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太低调了 和米田君怎么样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是小学时候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那日向你又怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 枫姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这一手啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到梦马郎就心跳不止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦马郎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦马~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸很长 看起来松软软的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:57.04,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,『岳人の歌』
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:57.04,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,登山者之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:10:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伴随星光的那个呼唤 从滑锁道那里传来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:10:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星がふるあのコールグリセードで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"那个人会来吗?" 嘴里衔着花想道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,あの人はくるかしら花をくわえて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔卑斯的恋歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,アルプスの恋唄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人心跳不已  回忆起那个登山者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心ときめくよ　なつかしの岳人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个温柔的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,やさしかのきみ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 振作点 我不会丢下你不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 我吃得太撑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放弃啊 马上到山顶了 两个人都变成万人...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:10:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 日向真是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害我睡不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就天亮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 你怎么这么早就起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我回忆起小时候 我们两人一起看日出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从富士山上看的话 会更美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大家一起住帐篷真是太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次要真在山上住就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.61,Next01,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(992.4,372.4)}待!续!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.61,Next02,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(992.4,372.4)}待!续!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:07.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}ねぇ～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:14.34,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}お互いの指と指、四角を作るなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:17.89,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}目の前の景色全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:21.90,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}切り取って、持ってけるかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:27.90,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}待ってたって見事、来ない今日の日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.93,0:00:32.09,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}空の青、感動の輪を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:35.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}顔見合わせて笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:38.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}そう、お揃いのプレゼント
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:42.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}泣いて笑った、precious days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:46.29,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}10年後、100年後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:49.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}色あせない思い出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:52.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}半分持ってて、Wow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:07.44,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:14.34,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}两人把手指比在一起 做成四角形
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:17.89,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}眼前全部景象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:21.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}能剪切下来 拿走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:27.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}坐立不安 期待这久久不来的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.93,0:00:32.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}蓝蓝的天 感动的圈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:35.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}看着对方的脸笑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:38.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}对 礼物都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:42.76,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}充满喜怒哀乐的那些特殊日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:46.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}10年后 100年后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:49.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}回忆也不会褪色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:52.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}两人互持一半 Wow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:04.72,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 不思議、どうしてかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:12.50,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}君が笑うと、心の奥いつもキラリ瞬く
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:15.06,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Dest will step 一歩ずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:18.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Dest will skip 一緒にね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:30.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}気がつけば、夢中になってた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:36.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}「そういう事あるよね？」って、言ってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:42.00,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}ギュッと手と手繋いだら、伝わる温もり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:46.84,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}どこにでも、行けちゃう気がしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:52.87,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tin ton tan、踏み出した瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:58.51,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}世界がパノラマみたいに、開けたの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:03.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile どんな、空の広さ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:09.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}一人きりじゃ、きっと気付けなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:14.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 笑顔、こだましてる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:22.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}胸に広がる優しい、嬉しい、新しい予感たち
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:28.44,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}一歩、一歩、進んで行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:04.72,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 真不可思议 为什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:12.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}你一笑起来 心里总会闪亮亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:15.06,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Dest will step 一步一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:18.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Dest will skip 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:30.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}回过神来 发现已经着迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:36.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}"这种事会有的吧?" 你这样说道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:42.00,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}紧紧地握住我的手 体温传达给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:46.84,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}不管去哪里 都感觉无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:52.87,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tin ton tan 跨出那一步的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:58.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}世界就像全景画一样 展开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:03.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 无论天空有多宽阔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:09.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}如果只有我一人 肯定不会在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:14.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 笑声回响在耳边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:22.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}心中充满温柔、愉悦的感觉 还有新的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:28.44,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}一步 一步 前进吧
